{"tid":2338272,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"南非變種版本的武漢肺炎病毒","createTime":"2020-12-24T02:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T05:16:01.000Z","uid":38861,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a970919f35c616f458b1ce201217a886a8a7c706","tid":2338272,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:15:59.000Z","msg":"被發現出現在南非地區的武肺病毒變種（501Y.V2），今終有文獻（Ref1)鈙述其相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n對比英國地區變種，501Y.V2在S protein的區域上多出兩道突變，K417N及E484K。<br />\n有證據顯示出，這兩道變異對於抗體與病毒的接觸有著一定的作用，其變異更有能力逃避由未變種病毒所產生出來的抗體，迴避抗體的能力比英國變種版本更勝一籌。<br />\n<br />\n現今疫苗廠商正忙於搜集證據自身的疫苗能否應對英國變種版本，但能否應對南非地區或未來將會展現出的變種版本，將成一大疑問。<br />\n<br />\n口罩及社交距離，顯然會在2021年繼續出現。<br />\n<br />\n醫治武肺的藥物究竟何時會出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.12.21.20248640v1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medrxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2020.12.21.20248640v1&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=2051be3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.12.21.20248640v1</a>"},{"pid":"a838f723d00e37992497b470e95aaed65c3bb482","tid":2338272,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"病毒變種得快定係藥出得快呢"},{"pid":"16e30d1e3df1b6b906b1950d6fc99dcaf6177f09","tid":2338272,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"點避 上面d受器已經唔同？"},{"pid":"948365c79d6cc80973582b6955ea8d9de7419205","tid":2338272,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a838f723d00e37992497b470e95aaed65c3bb482","tid":2338272,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"病毒變種得快定係藥出得快呢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"幾個月之前袁教授出過文章，對於醫治武肺的藥物有啲眉目，可能藥物依方面先係救星。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d9af01e4b43a3a2ac7a37a9b3